description: Welcome to my portfolio! I am a detail-oriented Computer Science professional with a Master's degree from CSUF, specializing in data structures, artificial intelligence, and machine learning. My academic journey and hands-on experiences have equipped me with a diverse skill set, including proficiency in Python, SQL, C/C++, and web technologies such as React and JavaScript. Explore my projects, showcasing my ability to apply theoretical knowledge to real-world challenges, and witness my dedication to delivering innovative solutions.
detailOrQuote: I am passionate about solving problems in new creative ways to drive innovation. By leveraging my coding experience I continually look for new and better ways to make tech accessible by all.
